            <p>
Seven of the eight items first edited in <bibl><ptr target="bib:VenkatasubbaAyyar1943_01"/></bibl> (SII 12, n° 23-A), with facsimile of five items. 
Edited and summarised in <bibl><ptr target="bib:Mahalingam1988_01"/></bibl> (IP 52).
This edition by Emmanuel Francis (2020), based on partial visual documentation, that is, the facsimile in <bibl><ptr target="bib:VenkatasubbaAyyar1943_01"/></bibl> and photographs of four items (2011).
            </p>

